@ddl-kartik-mathur it's worthwhile noting the dependencies Julia laid out and document it. If customers want to use async model APIs, DSE is no longer the way to go. 

For what it's worth, I have routinely 'apt-get installed' dependencies in tests and they have failed exactly once since 2020.

Hence, it's worthwhile merging this PR the way it is. Further, the compute environment's team might not have the bandwidth to create a new images and further maintain it for every release qualification.
